✅ Case Study 4: Jenkins Pipeline (Basic)
Where to write code:
👉 Pipeline Job → Pipeline Script

Code:
pipeline {
    agent any
    stages {
        stage('Build') {
            steps {
                echo 'Build Stage'
            }
        }
        stage('Test') {
            steps {
                echo 'Test Stage'
            }
        }
        stage('Deploy') {
            steps {
                echo 'Deploy Stage'
            }
        }
    }
}

