✅ Case Study 6: Real CI/CD Pipeline
Where to write code:
👉 Pipeline Job or Jenkinsfile

Sample Code:
pipeline {
    agent any
    stages {
        stage('Build') {
            steps {
                echo 'Building app'
            }
        }
        stage('Test') {
            steps {
                echo 'Running tests'
            }
        }
        stage('Deploy') {
            steps {
                echo 'Deploying app'
            }
        }
    }
    post {
        always {
            echo 'Pipeline completed'
        }
    }
}

